property.description: Nice location with convenient access to I-75, the turnpike, shops, entertainment, and dining. This charming two-bedroom unit features spacious walk-in closets, two full baths, inside unit stacked laundry, and a bonus or office room. The unit is equipped with accordion hurricane windows for added safety. Additional parking is available, and residents can enjoy the serene courtyard, inviting pool, and relaxing jacuzzi. Small outside Storage unit available. The Homeowners Association (HOA) boasts robust reserves, which includes water and more. It is important to note that rentals are not permitted, and a minimum credit score of 650 is required. The association allows 2 pets under 25 lbs. each. Verify pet fee amount with the association.
